cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.CL 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with deep generative models and their inference. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves the development of intelligent systems that can learn from data. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision) as the experiments involve image classification tasks. The paper also involves the use of Bayesian nonparametrics, which could place it under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) or cs.CL (Computation and Language).
